thread.title: Man arrested for killing California police officer, wounding another

title: Man arrested for killing California police officer, wounding another
text:
Man arrested for killing California police officer, wounding another 9:12am EDT - 00:52 
A California man was arrested Saturday after a 15-hour standoff with a police SWAT team. He was charged with killing one police officer and wounding another. Linda So reports.
